<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">在做减法时，如果被减数的末几位不够减，可先将减数分解成与被减数的末几位相同的数和另一个数，然后再一次减去这两个数，即得其结果。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">521-122=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">521-122</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=521-121-1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=400-1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=399</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>